title: MS SQL Server: Locks per Batch
agents: windows
catalog: app/mssql
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the number of lock requests in relation to the
 number of batch requests on the MSSQL server. Upper levels for the locks
 per batch ratio can be configured in Wato.

 This check needs the Checkmk mssql.vbs -plugin installed in
 the agent. Please refer to the online documentation
 for how to install that plugin.

item:
 Name of the database

inventory:
 One service is created for each instance.

cluster:
 On a cluster the check just cumulates all results for each cluster node.
 The overall result state then reflects the worst state of all nodes.
